From 00e0b9455fb4c74fc777289a129f646b4cb112f8 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mehdi Djait <mehdi.djait@linux.intel.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Jun 2025 15:51:16 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] media: v4l2-common: Add the missing Raw Bayer pixel formats
Git-commit: 00e0b9455fb4c74fc777289a129f646b4cb112f8
References: jsc#PED-14445
Patch-mainline: v6.17-rc1

Add the Raw Bayer pixel formats infos for:
10-bit packed Bayer formats
12-bit packed Bayer formats
14-bit Bayer formats
14-bit packed Bayer formats
16-bit Bayer formats

Signed-off-by: Mehdi Djait <mehdi.djait@linux.intel.com>
Reviewed-by: Laurent Pinchart <laurent.pinchart@ideasonboard.com>
Signed-off-by: Sakari Ailus <sakari.ailus@linux.intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Hans Verkuil <hverkuil@xs4all.nl>
Signed-off-by: Oliver Neukum <oneukum@suse.com>

---
 drivers/media/v4l2-core/v4l2-common.c | 20 ++++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 20 insertions(+)

diff --git a/drivers/media/v4l2-core/v4l2-common.c b/drivers/media/v4l2-core/v4l2-common.c
